data.description: Nestled amidst the tranquil Montlake neighborhood sits a spacious 5-bedroom home with plenty of room to enjoy. The interior features 3 fireplaces, upgraded flooring, and many windows for plenty of natural light. The home is over 2,600+ square feet and sits on a large lot of over 9,000+ Sqft! The exterior features a spacious fully fenced lot with plenty of parking & underground sprinklers. Montlake Park w/boat launch is a short 2-minute drive away! Call to schedule a private showing.
